reviewText: Wish they all came on cd for the car! My son loves all the songs!
Great product for truck loving toddler

We love these DVDs! Our boys will sing and dance to these for hours and I often catch myself singing along! The first 2 are great and this one is no exception! Your little (or big!) truck lover will enjoy it for years!

Purchased for my grandson to have movie time while at our house.  It's okay.  He's not really taken to it.  He is 3.  He LOVES all kinds of trucks, tracctors, moving machinery.  This is just a so so for him.  However, I don't feel its a bad video, just doesn't catch his attention like a few other ones we own.
We have truck tunes 1 and 2 and love this one too!!

We purchase all three truck tunes videos as our 4 year old was constantly watching them on YouTube and we thought this way he could watch them without using up all our data! LOL. The songs are extremely catchy and everyone in the family has been humming them since we got the videos. The little one loves them and couldn't be happier now that he doesn't have to wait his turn to get the iPad to watch the videos!
Super cute, clever and catchy tunes. My son can not get enough of these songs.
Very catchy songs and informative as well
My 3 year old absolutely loves this video !
I give it 5 stars b/c my 2 year old son LOVES it. The music drives me nuts, but I'm not the one it's directed toward :)
